ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇intern <br />\n係大公司做緊垃圾post <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd8f86fc9aea34d8a6c2547dd99cfa5d27492a1","tid":253372,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"上當年剩係報左學校intern schema , 無係出面搵<br />\n<br />\n其實有intern唔代表乜, 有時間學好英文仲好"},{"pid":"2f38cbfc8e59dac6b831025be0b878f70f5bad6c","tid":253372,"uid":4838,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上當年剩係報左學校intern schema , 無係出面搵<br />\n<br />\n其實有intern唔代表乜, 有時間學好英文仲好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">兩年前IELTS 8.0</span></span><br />\n乞食科連interview都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順道勸下各位DSE考生<br />\nJUPAS跟所謂興趣揀科就會好似我宜家既收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5a6e826c235bc8d1245b43aa621b5edc4fe6e6","tid":253372,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"Intern = 廉價勞工<br />\n如果唔係自己鐘意嘅工不如唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caae6ef0cd5c352fce3eb376be30c5c751619c31","tid":253372,"uid":66106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"三大商科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣都係無intern offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過反問自己intern係咪真係重要到無左會死，然後又問自己無又如何，個暑假其實攞黎玩下唔同比賽etc咁都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b345d6cfd8af56b72062e419e8d19ac7b6e7b3c","tid":253372,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十幾份會否太少<br />\n<br />\n利申：報咗30幾份有3份offer</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔應該鳩報<br />\n<br />\n你諗下自己有咩優勢<br />\n睇多幾份揀幾份真係自己有優勢既<br />\n正正經經寫封cover letter好過啦<br />\n<br />\n我都頹科 all in剩係報左2份 2份都有offer"},{"pid":"6c0306027953610a636611f1b1b57b082a63137d","tid":253372,"uid":4838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十幾份會否太少<br />\n<br />\n利申：報咗30幾份有3份offer</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔應該鳩報<br />\n<br />\n你諗下自己有咩優勢<br />\n睇多幾份揀幾份真係自己有優勢既<br />\n正正經經寫封cover letter好過啦<br />\n<br />\n我都頹科 all in剩係報左2份 2份都有offer</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n100%命中率<br />\n巴打有咩技巧可唔可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fba92914fcbaef6e888e82a60915415045ffeee","tid":253372,"uid":4838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三大商科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣都係無intern offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過反問自己intern係咪真係重要到無左會死，然後又問自己無又如何，個暑假其實攞黎玩下唔同比賽etc咁都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有咁諗過<br />\n但一來暑假唔返工keep住做野真係會好頹廢<br />\n雖然已經決定左如果無intern就學一樣想學既野<br />\n二來呢排太多負面情緒<br />\n唔返工只會不斷亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三來都想搵返少少錢<br />\n雖然宜家已經唔介意貼錢求offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9549ba353fb4d6f97fba89b2cca1cf44b29cea9c","tid":253372,"uid":17535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十幾份會否太少<br />\n<br />\n利申：報咗30幾份有3份offer</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔應該鳩報<br />\n<br />\n你諗下自己有咩優勢<br />\n睇多幾份揀幾份真係自己有優勢既<br />\n正正經經寫封cover letter好過啦<br />\n<br />\n我都頹科 all in剩係報左2份 2份都有offer</blockquote><br />\n我好有興趣知係邊兩份offer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6514c36d30914c398a9435bc0672f118dc22cdf4","tid":253372,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:15:54.000Z","msg":"Summer已經預咗做保安算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da127d1fd1d9f10b4f5549c6f5f7faf0dd417e4f","tid":253372,"uid":116240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三大乞食科<br />\ngpa過三<br />\n有exchange有上莊<br />\n整係Year2返過一份垃圾summer job<br />\n<br />\n今年報左十幾份intern<br />\n但大部分都無消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIn過個一兩間都完全無消息<br />\n咁既情況係咪人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇報政府？政府通常6月出intern offer，interview都唔洗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩post 唔洗interview<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74feeb00bea2f442a7c188777d5bc77e2186f6a","tid":253372,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三大乞食科<br />\ngpa過三<br />\n有exchange有上莊<br />\n整係Year2返過一份垃圾summer job<br />\n<br />\n今年報左十幾份intern<br />\n但大部分都無消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIn過個一兩間都完全無消息<br />\n咁既情況係咪人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇報政府？政府通常6月出intern offer，interview都唔洗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩post 唔洗interview<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多intern都唔洗, 見gpa就收, 公司根本唔得閒搞"},{"pid":"f6a4f3339b294c3da7789f842180ca93cb9d389f","tid":253372,"uid":4838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三大乞食科<br />\ngpa過三<br />\n有exchange有上莊<br />\n整係Year2返過一份垃圾summer job<br />\n<br />\n今年報左十幾份intern<br />\n但大部分都無消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.g